{"tid":604588,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"派股息養老","createTime":"2018-03-24T23:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T12:02:04.000Z","uid":53055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fd36da9eeda8758201abd69a72fb5c61e81fc6d7","tid":604588,"uid":53055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T23:35:22.000Z","msg":"今時今日香港仲可唔可以靠股息養老？<br />\n請各位前輩以5仔作為討論基礎<br />\n<br />\n住自己地方，水電煤雜費為固定支出。"},{"pid":"983958ac73d99c5ba989332547fb0f51db659a34","tid":604588,"uid":16061,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T23:51:29.000Z","msg":"你個本大咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f419d3de4e7c9de9d4bcb36e4aec0157913013a3","tid":604588,"uid":18948,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T23:57:02.000Z","msg":"你有一千幾百億淨係活期息養乜都夠啦"},{"pid":"3edd48513ea33222f6e4dcc1d938780e74c2a095","tid":604588,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f419d3de4e7c9de9d4bcb36e4aec0157913013a3","tid":604588,"uid":18948,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T23:57:02.000Z","msg":"你有一千幾百億淨係活期息養乜都夠啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T23:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e119812888c90aaec378da7b7fa08f7c49a07dd","tid":604588,"uid":17738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T00:00:50.000Z","msg":"要睇你想點「養老」法，如果只係計必須支出、例如食飯、水電煤等等費用嘅話<br />\n<br />\n持有嘅股票穩定派息、有增加派息嘅可以追到通貨膨脹，數量又夠冚呢堆消費就可以<br />\n<br />\n被動收入大過支出，退到休養到老，仲有餘錢享受餘下人生<br />\n<br />\n被動收入等如支出，退到休養到老，不過就未必可以去多幾次旅行，食好西<br />\n<br />\n被動收入細過支出，未退得休養到老"},{"pid":"8818f614e6649ddb425ccd33b84056b0160b99e3","tid":604588,"uid":129644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T00:01:25.000Z","msg":"你要先介定你養老既定義 <br />\n要幾多錢先夠你養老 年支出大概幾多<br />\n同埋你用黎投資既本金係幾多<br />\n仲有你係衣家要即刻養老定十年廿年後 <br />\n有以上資料先判斷到"},{"pid":"f433b01d149127971c4814071b2c02e597495e5f","tid":604588,"uid":17738,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T00:15:11.000Z","msg":"唔理你叫「養老」定「退休」，或者「上岸」都好，喺冇工作之後，30歲又好、70歲都好<br />\n<br />\n假設你唔係有一大嚿錢多過你由20歲開工到65歲嘅人工總和<br />\n<br />\n而你嘅資產可以產生嘅現金流足以冚到喺工作帶嚟嘅主動收入，又滿足於現時生活，咁就係<br />\n<br />\n我唔以年齡計「養老」嘅，70歲揸綠VAN嘅大有人在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不如改為「被動收入足夠生活唔再開工生活」似乎好啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf443cc91a728ca1132171bdb0c46d30f4a8453","tid":604588,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"一千萬買兩個單位收租<br />\n或者唔想煩買哂黎收息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287faf4db8721e20bb37a04b5a5a47868fa0b732","tid":604588,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"本細 冇乜用<br />\n不過好過放係銀行"},{"pid":"00ae6aa0c7ce2ad9f25b205909caa2482d62bf33","tid":604588,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"之前同事教我5號仔$5x個陣入左百幾手 <br />\n而家返工等派息<br />\n但同時又好想放出去 唔知點好"},{"pid":"de1cbbe4b602c842e0969d4f1398a0c37dde0633","tid":604588,"uid":118830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"00ae6aa0c7ce2ad9f25b205909caa2482d62bf33","tid":604588,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"之前同事教我5號仔$5x個陣入左百幾手 <br />\n而家返工等派息<br />\n但同時又好想放出去 唔知點好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:23:20.000Z","msg":"百幾手買到層樓"},{"pid":"1717984ef181e1e8213d56c88b3ff8b6520a4b0f","tid":604588,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:35:31.000Z","msg":"銀行係高風險行業"},{"pid":"915d60dfee84723333642b787eaf5e91fb32ce22","tid":604588,"uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T02:46:27.000Z","msg":"其實0003煤氣都唔錯？<br />\n雖然派息唔夠銀行股多，但如果係長期投資<br />\n佢既10股送1股呢個潛在增長都幾抵屌下？<br />\